data.title: Those Hip Hop Guys Radio | July 19th: New Snoop and SNYD & A.P.R.I.M.E. come thru to talk about their new projects
data.text:
By ,

On Tuesday's Those Hip Hop Guys Radio, we dropped a new joint by Snoop that was actually pretty fire. Also, SYND came through to talk about their new project '80zSoul' and APRIME came to talk his new joint '3099'.

Those Hip Hop Guys Radio airs every Tuesday Night on WMSE 91.7FM from 9-midnight. DJ Bizzon and Jank focus on underground and old school hip hop that you don't hear anywhere else on Milwaukee's airwaves. Stream live at www.wmse.org
